<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 13:26:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普 14 亿美元的收入使他成为美国最大的加密货币摇钱树</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-01/trump-s-1-4-billion-haul-makes-him-biggest-us-crypto-moneymaker</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普扭转了他早期对加密货币的怀疑，成为该行业最大的支持者之一，他去年报告的加密货币相关收入比任何一家上市的美国数字资产公司的收入都多。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iAjySQPN89S0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 16:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-01/trump-s-1-4-billion-haul-makes-him-biggest-us-crypto-moneymaker</guid></item><item><title>策略、加息担忧导致比特币跌至 21 个月低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-01/bitcoin-falls-to-21-month-low-on-strategy-rate-hike-fears</link><description>由于利率上升的前景以及对该代币最大企业买家的担忧削弱了市场情绪，比特币跌至 21 个月新低。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iwrKSepC.Aro/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 02:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-01/bitcoin-falls-to-21-month-low-on-strategy-rate-hike-fears</guid></item><item><title>迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 的比特币承诺在经济低迷时期兑现了现实</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-30/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-promise-meets-reality-during-downturn</link><description>战略的融资飞轮已断裂。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNbgIOgYPiRA/v7/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-30/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-promise-meets-reality-during-downturn</guid></item><item><title>策略抛售加剧焦虑，比特币跌破 60,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-30/bitcoin-slides-below-60-000-as-strategy-selloff-refuels-anxiety</link><description>周二，比特币暴跌 3.5%，跌至 58,000 美元，原因是投资者推翻了对 Strategy Inc. Michael Saylor 融资改革的初步信任投票，引发了人们对加密货币最大买家之一可能不再是持续需求来源的新担忧。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVwKogDxx6Ps/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 17:24:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-30/bitcoin-slides-below-60-000-as-strategy-selloff-refuels-anxiety</guid></item></channel></rss>